{"id":609432,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/04/【异闻观止】广电总局游戏新规：-打斗不能有任何/","date":"2019-04-22T07:52:05Z","modified":"2019-04-22T11:18:33Z","title":"【异闻观止】广电游戏新规：打斗不能有任何颜色液体出现","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-609433\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/8c9f916ccf384058a05cbf46d7734662.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/8c9f916ccf384058a05cbf46d7734662.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/8c9f916ccf384058a05cbf46d7734662-300x142.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>【广电总局游戏新规：#未成年人账号不能结婚#打斗不能有液体】4月22日起全国范围内将开放手里国产及进口游戏审批。新的版号申请注意事项显示游戏申请有了新变化，其中，要求打斗系统任何颜色液体都不能出现，包括绿色血液，尸体需尽快消失等。未成年人不能开放结婚系统，但可以享受结婚系统的收益。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-609435\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/38836cf1d1a243b985afb2a58b0df6ec.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"973\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/38836cf1d1a243b985afb2a58b0df6ec.jpeg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/38836cf1d1a243b985afb2a58b0df6ec-170x300.jpeg 170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-609434\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/2f701c45311941d6af1e56dcfe411fc1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"786\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/2f701c45311941d6af1e56dcfe411fc1.jpeg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/04/2f701c45311941d6af1e56dcfe411fc1-210x300.jpeg 210w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":210,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,20505],"tags":[9249,9254]}